## Three-layer responsibility (R3)

| Layer       | File                       | MUST do                                                                 | MUST NOT do                                          |
|-------------|----------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|
| Service     | `service.py`               | Instantiate scraper, dispatch action, pass `(ctx, params)` through       | Network, schema mapping, import `crawler._internal.*`|
| Scraper     | `crawler/scraper.py`       | Pagination, merge, iteration, write via `ctx.write_record(Model.to_dict())` | HTTP, signing, cookie parsing                        |
| Client      | `crawler/client.py`        | HTTP/WSS protocol work, signing, cookie injection, single-request/client retries | Multi-request orchestration, schema mapping          |
| Models      | `crawler/models.py`        | `@dataclass`, `from_raw()` helpers, `to_dict()`                         | Network calls, `TaskContext` access                  |
| `_internal/`| `crawler/_internal/*`      | Platform-private helpers (cookie / sign / parse)                        | Be imported from `service.py` / `bridge.py`          |

