## Verifying your changes

Run any of these any time — they're cheap:

```bash
# Static contract check (all platforms)
python tests/test_platform_conformance.py

# Just this one
python tests/test_platform_conformance.py --platform {{platform_name}}

# pytest-driven (CI gate)
pytest tests/test_platform_conformance.py -k {{platform_name}}

# Shape / schema check
python -m crawlhub.scripts.verify_crawlers --only {{platform_name}}
```

A green run means your crawler obeys the platform conformance gate,
including schema/dataclass matching, service thinness, runtime/transport
metadata, and WebSocket stop-condition contracts. The daemon will register
it on next start.

